item.title: 449 - Brian's been breadboarding with Brent Mason
item.description:
Brian, Blake, and Richard are back for an all-new episode of the Chasing Tone Podcast!

The saga of Brian's use of Chat GPT to avoid him ever having to communicate with other human beings continues, much to the annoyance of Richard, and the guys look at the issue of who owns the intellectual property to AI generated material... item.title: Corruption in the Family
item.description: Families can go wrong. And unless you've been under a rock these last weeks, you'll know that a number of members of the Socialist family at the European Parliament went very wrong.
